o perform the optimization.\n- n_jobs: Number of parallel jobs (-1 uses all available cores).\n- noise_tolerance: A threshold to filter noise in the objective function evaluation.\n- annealing_factor: Factor by which the search space is reduced during each refinement iteration."]}, {"name": "acon.gradient_slice_sorting.GSSOptimizer.optimize", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Perform the optimization using the GSS method.\n\nReturns:\n- best_params: The best set of parameters found.\n- best_score: The best score achieved by those parameters."]}, {"name": "acon.gradient_slice_sorting.GSSOptimizer._initial_split_param_space", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Split the parameter space into initial slices.\n\nReturns:\n- slices: A list of tuples representing the sliced parameter spaces."]}, {"name": "acon.gradient_slice_sorting.GSSOptimizer._split_dimension", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "param_range", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "num_slices", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Split a single dimension of the parameter space.\n\nReturns:\n- slices: A list of tuples representing the slices in this dimension."]}, {"name": "acon.gradient_slice_sorting.GSSOptimizer._sample_points", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "param_slice", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Sample random points within the given slice of the parameter space.\n\nReturns:\n- points: A list of sampled points (each a list of values for each dimension)."]}, {"name": "acon.gradient_slice_sorting.GSSOptimizer._sort_points_by_objective", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "points", "ty